An overview of Tesla's Gigafactory in Shanghai over the weekend. Tesla global vice president Tao Lin said on Monday that the Shanghai factory is ready for production and sales will begin after gaining product certifications and government approval. Tesla plans to assemble at least 1,000 of its Model 3s each week in the Chinese factory. Photo:VCG  
